            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">Ap</supplied>olli<lb break="no" n="2"/>naris dupl<lb break="no" n="3"/>arius <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> pro s<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>lute sua et <lb n="6"/>conmani<lb break="no" n="7"/>pulorum <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Pio et Proculo co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 9 befindet sich auf der crepido. Z. 3: Querhaste über den II der Legionsnummer; Z. 4: AD-Ligatur.</p>
            </div>
